Lambda 

--> aws serverless service. Doesnt need any server to run.Underline infrastructure AWS manage karta hai
--> sns(message ata hai it is event)/sqs/s3(file upload/delete is event) se subscribed kar sakte hai and lambda invoke hota hai
--> in our company, devops teams has written automated pipelines where they pull the code(eventHandler class path) from our git repo and put in the created lambda.(zip/jar/from s3)
--> SNSEvent --> SNS records --> extract message from it to process.
--> max runtime is 15 min aws hard limit

